      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-grade condition. This specimen features the legendary S54B32 power plant, showcasing flawless compression across all six cylinders and a documented VANOS system overhaul. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission provides crisp, mechanical shifts, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential for optimal torque vectoring. This vehicle boasts a reinforced rear subframe\u2014a critical prophylactic measure\u2014and pristine suspension bushings that maintain original kinematic precision. The factory finish is devoid of micro-marring, and the undercarriage remains free of any oxidation or fluid seepage. A mechanically synchronic example for the discerning purist.",
