    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle that remains in absolute showroom condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, ensuring the factory paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster without a single stone chip or swirl mark in sight. The interior is a masterclass in care; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and the cabin still carries that signature new-car aroma. Every feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the precision climate control, operates exactly as it did the day it was delivered. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by master technicians using OEM parts. With a documented service history and zero exposure to inclement weather, this car offers the rare opportunity to own a piece of automotive perfection. It drives tight, quiet, and powerful, offering a 'time capsule' experience for the most discerning enthusiast.",
